modName: Chryllian son of the Witch preset
summary: Preset of a Nord character, that I am pretty satisfied with.
descriptionHtml:
To install drop the file into Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets

Requirements:
Racemenu

For him to look the same youll need:
KS Hairdos - Renewal
Eyes of Aber
Northborn Scars
Freckle Mania
body scars for racemenu
SR Freckles
Fine Face Textures for Men

I use the Schlongs of Skyrim bodytype with Smooth Male Body textures

Enjoy :)

Thanks to [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/2950481]expired6978[/url] for creating Racemenu.
